item.title: Ubuntu
item.description: Ubuntu Ubuntu is a free and open-source Linux-based operating system developed by Canonical and a community of developers. It’s a popular choice for desktop, server, and IoT devices. Ubuntu is known for its user-friendly interface, wide range of software, and strong community support.
